com.devtence.will.dev.endpoints

Class BaseController<T extends BaseModel>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.devtence.will.dev.endpoints.BaseController<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type that extends BaseModel
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuthorAPI, CategoryAPI, ClientsAPI, ConfigurationsAPI, ContentAPI, LanguageAPI, NotificationsAPI, RoleAPI, UsersAPI

    public abstract class BaseController<T extends BaseModel>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract Class created to serve as the base for the controllers that use Google App Engine to define endpoints. Defines basic methods every model must have, and implements the basic functions to validate an user.

    Every class that extends from this will use the UserAuthenticator class as default authenticator.

    Since:
    2016-06-02
    Author:
    plessmann

        Base method to get a segmented and sorted list of elements of type T.

        limit - max elements for the segment
        sortFields - array of strings with the names of the fields to be used to sort the data
